*   **Data-Hypothesis Alignment**: The dataset lacks granular intra-day data. Daily OHLCV is insufficient to distinguish between "dispersion due to idiosyncratic news" and "dispersion due to liquidity-driven fragility." You are attempting to infer high-frequency microstructure phenomena from low-frequency daily aggregates.
